Product name: Shower Steamer - Shower Soother - Sinus Relief - Shower Melt - Shower Bomb - Shower Steamers - Shower Tablet - Shower Bombs -Eucalyptus
Description:
Stuffy nose? Sinus Problems? Sick and tired of being sick? Breath Easy Shower Steamers are perfect for you. These shower steamers are packed with soothing eucalyptus, peppermint and rosemary essential oils with added benefits of menthol crystals. This blend is perfect for clearing your nose and sinuses.
Drop one of these wonderful shower tablets into the bottom of a nice warm shower or on a shower shelf and as it dissolves it will slowly releases its wonderful soothing aromatherapy vapors.
Alternative use- Fill a large bowl with hot water. Place the shower steamer into the water and sit closely to enjoy the natural vapors created while the shower steamer is dissolving. 
This listing is for a set of 3 or 6 shower steamers. Each shower bomb is individually wrapped and stored in the pouch as shown above.

Product name: Engraved Renaissance Emerald Wedding Set, Custom Oxidized Silver Engagement Ring, Lab Emerald Jewelry, Green Gemstone Bridal Set
Description:
Made to Order Oxidized Silver & Lab Grown Emerald Wedding Set
Turnaround Time: 7 Business Days  Shipping (1-2 weeks to the Asia-Pacific region and 2-3 weeks to most other locations)
This handmade wedding set features a lovely 8mm round lab grown emerald set in an sterling silver crown bezel upon an sterling silver band. The emerald is a beautiful vibrant green. The ring bands have a floral, leafy Renaissance inspired pattern and are each 3.4mm wide. The wedding band has had a spot filed flat in the pattern to fit neatly beside the gemstone ring under the stone - see photo 4 for an example of the filed section.
The rings have been oxidized and lightly polished for a dramatic look. If you prefer these rings with a shiny silver finish instead please let us know in the Notes to Seller box.
We can offer a customized engraved message such as a special phrase or important date on the inside of the ring bands for you. You can see our font choices in the last picture. If you would like your rings engraved just select the Engraving Variation with your chosen font from the drop down menu, and mention the phrase you want engraved in the 'optional note to seller' section at checkout. Please make sure your message is 20 characters or less per ring--if you need your engraved message to be longer, please contact us first to make sure it will fit!
Oxidization can fade over time but is easy to reapply - we provide written advice with each order.
Your order will be shipped in a protective box & come with a mini ring-care kit. Please read our policies page prior to purchase. All orders are insured against loss or damage in transit, and a signature will be required on delivery of your order. Please allow up to seven business days for us to make this emerald bridal set.
Shipping times average 1-2 weeks to the Asia-Pacific region and 2-3 weeks to most other locations, depending on Customs processing times & postal services. You may be charged an import duty/tax on products over a certain value. These are levied by your government--please see our policies page for more information.
Not sure of your ring size? Leave a note and we will email you a copy of our measuring guide.
